sequenceDiagram
    participant DataIngestion
    participant FeatureEngineering
    participant ModelTraining
    participant ModelValidation
    participant EdgeDeployment
    participant Vehicle
    
    DataIngestion->>FeatureEngineering: Raw Sensor Data
    FeatureEngineering->>FeatureEngineering: Data Cleaning & Transformation
    FeatureEngineering->>ModelTraining: Prepared Features
    
    ModelTraining->>ModelTraining: Train Deep Learning Models
    ModelTraining->>ModelValidation: Trained Model
    
    ModelValidation->>ModelValidation: Safety Validation Tests
    
    alt Model Passes Validation
        ModelValidation->>EdgeDeployment: Deploy to Edge
        EdgeDeployment->>Vehicle: Update Model
        Vehicle->>DataIngestion: Feedback Data
    else Model Fails Validation
        ModelValidation->>ModelTraining: Retrain Required
    end
    
    Note over Vehicle: Real-time inference for<br/>autonomous driving decisions